# 🚀 Neva Chatbot — VPS Deployment Guide

**Target:** Ubuntu 24.04 (Hostinger VPS) • Subdomain: `neva.nevas.ai` • Nginx (already installed)
**AI Provider:** Google Gemini API (free tier) — no Ollama needed

